BEGIN_TEXT
Find the time required for an investment of 1 dollars to grow to $a
dollars at an interest rate of 7.5 percent per year, compounded quarterly.
$BR
Your answer is \(t=\) \{ans_rule(15) \} years.
$BR
END_TEXT

